Yorba_Linda.KFSH-FM: KFSH-FM (95.9 FM, "95.9 The Fish") is a contemporary Christian music radio station serving the far southern Los Angeles & Orange County, California metropolitan area. The station is owned by the Salem Media Group and the branding, 'The Fish', is a reference to the ichthys, the ancient fish icon used by the Christian church from its birth during the Roman Empire to the present. The icon itself is part of the station logo.
